name: Key world
description:
signonsis
Enjoy a great platform adventure in the world of Key World, enter a world with enemies, dangers, jumps, coins, keys, diamonds and traps that will entertain you, focus on trying to pass each level if you can, give your best effort

instructions
Play in your desktop web browser, not available for mobile phones, this platform game has simple controls explained in the loading menu.

Thank you

For the user who has decided to enter this page if they like this game, share it with their friends and, if you wish, you can collaborate so that this game reaches its full version and more future levels.
